---
title: "Daily digest pipeline (target / Planned)"
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant Cron as Digest Scheduler (08:00 UTC)
    participant Orch as Orchestrator (LangGraph)
    participant Src as Source agents (HN/ArXiv/YT/News)
    participant Mem as Mem0 profile
    participant Rank as Rank + FlashRank
    participant TG as Telegram

    Cron->>Orch: trigger daily digest
    Orch->>Src: asyncio.gather() — fetch last 24h
    Src-->>Orch: ArticleList (all sources)
    Orch->>Mem: load personal profile
    Mem-->>Orch: interests / weights
    Orch->>Rank: score relevance × novelty × quality
    Rank-->>Orch: top 5 insights
    Orch->>TG: send digest (5 ranked insights)
    TG-->>Orch: delivered
